name: Employee_Management_System_Microservices
description: An Employee Management System built with Spring Boot microservices architecture for efficient handling of employee and department data. Features include RESTful APIs for easy integration, service discovery with Eureka, and load balancing for scalability.

name: OrderProcessingSystem
description: This project is a microservices application for order creation, utilizing Kafka for order information transmission. The Payment Service processes orders, manages payments, and reports results via Kafka, while the Notification Service sends payment notifications to users.

name: mic-binpackingproblem-adapter

name: AgileShop
description: Microservice-based E-commerce Backend  AgileShop is a robust, scalable, and flexible e-commerce backend system built using microservices architecture. This project leverages TypeScript, Node.js, and Express to create a modular and efficient platform for handling various e-commerce operations.

name: Credit-Card-Score-Simulation
description: This project focuses on creating and deploying a credit scoring model to evaluate loan applicants' creditworthiness. It includes developing a machine learning model, deploying it as a microservice on AWS, and implementing monitoring and alerting systems to maintain reliability and performance.
